354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30afa251049d64888bdb753724c7a6b4c9e1c7b1","tid":2338065,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:02:13.000Z","msg":"馬狗 政府有權還押黎智英<br />\n張狗 關押合乎比例原則<br />\n李狗 社會處於緊急情況<br />\n霍狗 黎智英派錢搞港獨(假新聞)<br />\n賀狗 已在人身自由和社會安全取得平衡<br />\n<br />\n5比0 黎智英不可以保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdf69a5f6648f1a2c19a3e0289875194b091e88","tid":2338065,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa6681d477b1b59ab1b6ed201f72b779a451fe9","tid":2338065,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:43:38.000Z","msg":"唔好太老定話根據案例律政司衰硬<br />\n李義的對錯相對論就已經係明顯歸邊投向極權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"李義喺終院案例Dizon v HKSAR (FAMP2/09)嘅判詞講到咁：<br />\n<br />\n//...Under section 31 of the Court&rsquo;s statute, <span class=\"red\"><strong>the Court has a discretion to grant leave to appeal only from any final decision of the Court of First Instance from which no appeal lies to the Court of Appeal. </strong></span>A final decision in that context must mean the lower court&rsquo;s substantive decision disposing one way or another of the offence charged. <span class=\"red\"><strong>A bail application does not involve any such determination. A decision to refuse or grant bail is not final. Bail granted can be revoked.</strong></span> ...//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=68971&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch_result_detail_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D68971%26QS%3D%252B%26TP%3DJU&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MdG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=3adc53d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=68971&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單講 終院只會處理下級法院作出嘅final decision <br />\n而保釋申請不論個官批准定拒絕都唔算係final decision <br />\n因為拒絕咗個被告都可以按情況變化再申請過保釋 批准咗亦可以由個官按情況取消個保釋 結論就係終院唔會處理下級法院有關保釋申請決定嘅上訴<br />\n<br />\n李義當年喺判詞講到咁 我都想見識吓佢今日可以用乜嘢ground嚟推翻到昨日嘅自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b864df39ff3c25ad68fa0992bcb6d3e6c5407d","tid":2338065,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎尋晚搞到咁夜先有餐好既食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fa5f3dbd1184e0cc23763c88f3088ec87c226b","tid":2338065,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673d492c20b5adb4f87e604c176e375129ce813d","tid":2338065,"uid":109570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebdf69a5f6648f1a2c19a3e0289875194b091e88","tid":2338065,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa6681d477b1b59ab1b6ed201f72b779a451fe9","tid":2338065,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:43:38.000Z","msg":"唔好太老定話根據案例律政司衰硬<br />\n李義的對錯相對論就已經係明顯歸邊投向極權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"李義喺終院案例Dizon v HKSAR (FAMP2/09)嘅判詞講到咁：<br />\n<br />\n//...Under section 31 of the Court&rsquo;s statute, <span class=\"red\"><strong>the Court has a discretion to grant leave to appeal only from any final decision of the Court of First Instance from which no appeal lies to the Court of Appeal. </strong></span>A final decision in that context must mean the lower court&rsquo;s substantive decision disposing one way or another of the offence charged. <span class=\"red\"><strong>A bail application does not involve any such determination. A decision to refuse or grant bail is not final. Bail granted can be revoked.</strong></span> ...//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=68971&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch_result_detail_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D68971%26QS%3D%252B%26TP%3DJU&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MdG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=3adc53d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=68971&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單講 終院只會處理下級法院作出嘅final decision <br />\n而保釋申請不論個官批准定拒絕都唔算係final decision <br />\n因為拒絕咗個被告都可以按情況變化再申請過保釋 批准咗亦可以由個官按情況取消個保釋 結論就係終院唔會處理下級法院有關保釋申請決定嘅上訴<br />\n<br />\n李義當年喺判詞講到咁 我都想見識吓佢今日可以用乜嘢ground嚟推翻到昨日嘅自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"話就話common law and case law enshrines the feature of continuity. 但係CFA都話過自己係可以推翻之前既decision. 依加有國安法，都係唔好咁老定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1edc8acd4c1228d724488781d4cbfc7ddf0e37","tid":2338065,"uid":27986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30afa251049d64888bdb753724c7a6b4c9e1c7b1","tid":2338065,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:02:13.000Z","msg":"馬狗 政府有權還押黎智英<br />\n張狗 關押合乎比例原則<br />\n李狗 社會處於緊急情況<br />\n霍狗 黎智英派錢搞港獨(假新聞)<br />\n賀狗 已在人身自由和社會安全取得平衡<br />\n<br />\n5比0 黎智英不可以保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T23:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bou